<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: THE BURDEN OF PROOF BY SCOTT TUROW (FARRAR, STRAUS &amp; 
GIROUX: $22.95; 756 PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
