<P>
A MOTTO FOR COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Orange County's motto: As long as I have mine, to hell with everyone else! 
</P>
<P>
I guess it should come as no surprise that, once again, Orange County, the 
bastion of conservatism, greed and self-indulgence, goes against the homeless 
bond (Proposition 107) and two education bonds -- school districts (Proposition 
121) and higher education (Proposition 123) -- while the rest of the state 
