</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; CONGRESS (U.S.); LEGISLATORS; 
HONORARIUMS; TRAVEL; PERKS; SPECIAL INTEREST GROUPS; LOBBYING; DEFENSE INDUSTRY 
-- CALIFORNIA 
</P>
