DICK TRACY (MOTION PICTURE) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061790-0128 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 234904 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 17, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
