<HEADLINE>
<P>
PARKER AND POLL BATTLE AT FORUM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Edward (Pee Wee) Parker of Houston faces Jesus Poll of Los Angeles for the 
vacant International Boxing Council 126-pound junior championship Monday night 
at the Forum. 
</P>
<P>
Parker brings a 20-4-2 record with eight knockouts into the scheduled 12-round 
fight. Poll is 21-3-3 with four KOs. Both fighters are coming off losses. 
</P>
