MacMurray and Carroll O'Connor Viacom Enterprises; Photo, COLOR, (Cover) Bill 
Cosby NBC; Photo, COLOR, (Cover) Homer Simpson 20th Century Fox.; Photo, TV 
dads of the past, clockwise from above: Robert Young, ; Photo, Carl Betz, ; 
Photo, Hugh Beaumont. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
