<HEADLINE>
<P>
DAMEWORTH THIRD IN INVITATIONAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bryan Dameworth of Agoura High placed third in the two-mile in the 
International Prep Invitational track and field meet in Elmhurst, Ill., 
Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
Dameworth finished in 9 minutes 4.24 seconds. 
</P>
<P>
Shawn Mackay of East Elgin Secondary School in Canada won the event in 9:00.76 
and Andy Maris of White River High in Buckley, Wash., was second in 9:01.62. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
