BEHAVIOR; YOUTH; UNITED STATES -- CULTURE; EMPLOYMENT -- UNITED STATES; 
LIFESTYLES; DYCHTWALD, KEN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061790-0190 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 235062 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 17, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 2; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
