<P>
Joseph Dumars Jr., father of Detroit Piston guard Joe Dumars, was buried at 
Natchitoches, La., as more than 1,500 people jammed the auditorium, television 
reporters and photographers recorded the event and the procession behind the 
hearse stretched for nearly a mile. 
</P>
