JERRY HULSE'S TRAVEL TIPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
For the Record: In last week's Travel Tips, an item on home stays in the Soviet 
Union, arranged through Laguna Beach-based Traveling Shoes, said land 
arrangements cost $1,400 for one week. The price actually covers two weeks. For 
more information, call (714) 752-9036. 
</P>
