<DOCID> 235191 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 17, 1990, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 6; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
