borrows a mortarboard from her aunt, UCI engineering major Kathleen Schreiner, 
at Saturday's commencement. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Biological sciences major Julie Bozanich blows bubbles. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
