numbers. ; Photo, In his Garden Grove office, retired Air Force Col. Jack 
Bailey of Operation Rescue tries to resolve the status of missing U.S. 
servicemen. DAVID MURONAKA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
